<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fli-Alchemist Guide</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/styles.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image" href="images/bone_dragon.jpg" alt="Fantasy Life i Logo and Scenery Art">
</head>

<body class="main-page">
    <div class="content-wrapper">

        <header>
            <h1>Alchemist</h1>
        </header>

        <!-- Separated sections by title and then posted relevant information within each category -->
        <main>
            <h2 class="adjust-me">Gameplay</h2>


            <p>
                The Alchemist is a Life you can choose in the game Fantasy Life. It is one of 12 Lives that can be
                chosen at any time during the game by visiting the Guild Master (except during a story mission).

                The Alchemist uses flasks to make medicine, bombs, flasks and accessories. There are 67 alchemist
                recipes in the
                base game and 90 with the DLC.
            </p>

            <h2>Skills</h2>

            <p>
                When the player chooses the Alchemist life, they learn 3 skills: Alchemy, Compound Alchemy, and
                Accessory Alchemy.
                The max skill level is 15 (20 with the DLC). To unlock the new cap, you must reach Legend rank and talk
                to Divinus
                with the Alchemist Life activated. He will increase the cap of all 3 skills to 20 and upgrade the
                licence to
                God-in-Training rank.
            </p>

            <!-- Form section for looking up recipes on the mariadb -->
            <form method="post" action="submitted-recipes">
                <fieldset class="craft-selection">
                    <legend>Alchemist Recipes</legend>
                    <select id="alch_recipe" name="recipe_name">
                        <option value='none'>-- Select a Recipe --</option>
                        <option value='hp potion'>Hp potion</option>
                        <option value='sp potion'>Sp potion</option>
                        <option value='poison antidote'>Poison antidote</option>
                        <option value='stun antidote'>Stun antidote</option>
                    </select>


                    <button type="submit" class="main-button">Get Recipe</button>
                </fieldset>
            </form>

            <!-- Form section for user to submit recipes that are not inputted into the mariadb -->
            <h2>Missing Recipe</h2>

            <p>
                Data for the game is collected at the pace of whenever I'm able to play (which isn't often). If you see
                a recipe that isn't included in the option above, feel free to submit it for review! I'll take a look
                and add it to the database once it's determined that it's valid.
            </p>

            <form method="post" action="missing-recipes">

                <fieldset class="missing_recipe">
                    <legend>Alchemy Recipe</legend>
                    <label for="recipe_name">Recipe Name:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="recipe_name" name="recipe_name" placeholder="Enter recipe">

                    <label for="main_resource">Main Resource:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="main_resource" name="main_resource" placeholder="Enter resource">

                    <label for="main_quantity">Main Quantity:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="main_quantity" name="main_quantity" placeholder="Enter quantity">

                    <label for="sec_resource">Secondary Resource:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="sec_resource" name="sec_resource" placeholder="Enter resource">

                    <label for="sec_quantity">Secondary Quantity:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="sec_quantity" name="sec_quantity" placeholder="Enter quantity">

                    <label for="opt_reagent">Optional Reagent:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="opt_reagent" name="opt_reagent" placeholder="Enter reagent">

                    <label for="opt_quantity">Optional Reagent Quantity:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="opt_quantity" name="opt_quantity" placeholder="Enter quantity">

                    <br>

                    <button type="submit" class="main-button">Submit Recipe</button>
                </fieldset>
            </form>
        </main>


        <aside>
            <h3>Site Navigation</h3>
            <nav class="main-nav">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Home Page</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </aside>
    </div>


    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 www.fli-guide.com</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>